inn1.comm: it has been pushed towards mid-on.
on the middle stump line again, worked to midwicket
moves away from the off stump, Watson tries to slash it away but can't connect. Both the batsmen go gardening down the track and have a chat
lands on a length on the middle and leg, curves in towards middle, Sehwag shapes to play it to the on side but adjusts to the movement and pushes it back to the bowler
just outside off, from a length, goes hard into his forcing shot on the off side and edges it to the leg side
crash. It was a back-of-a-length delivery outside off, Sehwag shifted his weight to the back foot and punched it on the up and past the diving point fielder.
slips his first delivery down the leg side, gets past the attempted flick and Paine collects
bit of drama there. Tendulkar was shaping to let go a length delivery outside off but he was late on it; the ball ran off the face of the bat towards Ponting at second slip
in the zone outside off stump, goes on straight, good bounce and carry through to the keeper
leans forward to drive to the off side.
full in length, homing in on the off stump, Tendulkar eases it towards cover.
That typical wristy shot through the on side. He waits for the ball to drift in to him before he flicked it through the on side. Crowd roar in delight.
fuller, on the middle and off, Tendulkar shapes to drive it straight, the bat-face shuts a touch and the ball rolls towards mid-on
similar delivery to the last one from the previous over that Tendulkar hit to mid-on. But Sehwag manages to punch-drive it to the left of mid-on and it races away on this fast outfield
lands it on a good length this time and Sehwag pushes it to the off side
outside off stump and Sehwag tries to carve it away through point but doesn't make contact. Huge noise around the stadium.
bangs it in short, climbs around the off stump, Sehwag gets on top of the bounce to push it down towards mid-off
high harmless bouncer, Sehwag allows it to pass over him
on a length, around the middle and off line, punched towards mid-off
drifts down the leg side, Sehwag misses a chance to pick up a boundary as he fails to connect with the glance shot and Paine mops up
fetches it from around off stump and drags his drive towards square-leg. He went too hard into the shot and the bottom-hand came too much into the equation and ruined the shot
short in length, moving towards the hips, tucked behind square-leg for a single
bangs it in short, lifting delivery around the off stump and Tendulkar drops his wrists, gets the bat away from the line as he sways away

Siddle takes out SRT. Full in length, outside off, luring Tendulkar across but it straightens to take the edge. Full length delivery after the bouncer does the trick. Tendulkar played away from the body there, much like in the first game. What a lovely start from Siddle.
lifting delivery onto the ribcage, Gambhir hops to fend it away ungainly to the off side
another bouncer, climbs shoulder high, Gambhir takes his eyes off the ball and ducks; the ball bounds off the right shoulder to the off side. Ouch

and in comes the full length delivery outside off. Gambhir doesn't chase it. Good pace, carry and bounce on this track so far. Lovely stadium this, one of the best, if not the best, in the country. Nice bucket seats all around.

it was on the off stump but it was short in length and that allowed Sehwag to clip it from there through midwicket. He hopped back, gave himself more time and played it very neatly. A short midwicket comes in now.
moves in towards middle and leg, tucked behind square for a single
from very close to the stumps, on the middle and off line, shaping away, defended to short cover
on the middle, tilting in towards middle and leg, pushed out wide of midwicket for a single
high bouncer on the leg and middle line, climbs over Sehwag who ducks

slower one, aroudn 125 kmph delivery on the middle and leg, Sehwag waited before heaving it over square-leg. he stays adjacent to the line, doesn't go towards the ball and that allows him to pick the slower one better
fuller, on the middle stump line, driven crisply back down the track
it angles away from Gambhir who shoulders arms
fuller, draws Gambhir forward and it has been mistimed to short cover. Good ball that. Gambhir was late in getting forward and across and played away from the body.
But this time he is ready and springs to the front foot very quickly. He glided forward and drove it superbly between the umpire and the non-striker.
full again, driven to right of mid-off
on the middle stump, straightening, Sehwag shapes to work it to the on side but gets a leading edge to point.
cuts in towards middle and off and Sehwag leans forward to play a very solid defensive shot
lands on a length, comes in, Gambhir taps it to the on side for a single
lifting delivery on the middle and leg, Sehwag jumps, gets on top of the bounce and defends it down to the on side
on the middle and leg, bouncing delivery, worked to midwicket
drifts to the pads and all Gambhir had to do was get bat on ball; he does and the ball races to fine-leg boundary
leans forward to defend to midwicket
banged in short on the middle, Gambhir goes down under
big swing and a miss. Full in length and outside off stump, Sehwag went for his flamboyant cover drive but couldn't connect
fuller, around the off stump line, Sehwag doesn't go as hard as he did the previous delivery, preferring to time it past the diving cover fielder
lovely lifting delivery around off stump, Gambhir sways away from the line and Paine fumbles while trying to collect it from front of his face
another short delivery, this one flies over the middle and leg and Sehwag ducks
on the off stump line, straightens, Sehwag shapes to punch-drive, opens the bat-face to adjust to the straightening and the ball runs down to third man
on the middle and leg, defended to the on side
full in length, on the off stump line, punched away to mid-off
short and just outside off, Sehwag opens the bat-face and guides it down to third man
full delivery, on the middle, tilting in, flicked to fine-leg region for a single
short in length, bounces towards the off stump, Sehwag gets back to defend it back down the track
Smashing hit. It was full pitched delivery and Sehwag lifted it cleanly and hit it over long-on. Lovely clean full swing of the bat.
leans forward to play a very compact defensive stroke to a length delivery
short delivery, climbs outside off, Sehwag tries to upper cut it but doesn't connect
short in length, angling away from Gambhir who runs it down to third man
Flashed past the lone slip. It was a length delivery well outside off, Sehwag reached out for the flashy cut but edged it well past White at slip
fuller, on the middle and leg, on driven to right of mid-on where Hauritz makes a tumbling stop . Sehwag would feel he has missed out there... bit more away from Hauritz and he would have got a four
the bouncer on the leg and middle line, Gambhir ducks. Sehwag comes out for bit of gardening, he says something to Gambhir who nods
fuller, on the leg and middle line, Gambhir made sure his balance was good as he leaned forward and flicked it to the left of square-leg fielder.
lands on a length just outside leg, moves in to leg and middle, Gambhir tries to wrist it to square-leg but edges it down the track to the bowler

What a soft dismissal!  It was a full length delivery around the off stump line, Sehwag went for the big airy drive but mistimed it completely and sends a dolly of a catch to mid-off. It was outside off and Sehwag ended up slicing his drive; the bat-face turned in his hand
really full delivery, pushed down to mid-on
leans forward to defend this one
banged in short, climbs outside off stump and Yuvraj sways away
pushes it well outside off, inviting Yuvraj to drive but he resists
overpitched delivery on the legs, flicked away to deep midwicket for a single
on the middle and leg, Yuvraj goes back to play it to the on side but gets a leading edge to point. The ball was briefly in the air but fell short of any fielders
drifts to the pads, glanced past short fine-leg fielder for couple of runs
full in length, on the off, defended back down the track and he then wanders to the on side
on the middle and leg, full, Yuvraj wrists it neatly through wide midwicket. The line has been wrong this over so far
on the middle and leg again, pushed wide of midwicket for a single
slower one, off cutter, on the middle, tapped to point
full pitched on the legs and Yuvraj flicks it uppishly to deep square-leg boundary.. Again wrong line; they have given away two easy boundaries to Yuvraj now
another poor delivery , full toss on the legs, Yuvraj misses out; flicks it straight to deep midwicket
short in length, around the off stump this time, tapped down to third man
again going down leg side, Yuvraj fails to connect with the flick and Paine gathers
banged in short outside off stump, Yuvraj tries to upper cut it over slips but no wood on leather
back of length, on the off stump line, defended to the off side
full in length, in the channel outside off - his best delivery yet in this over- left alone
on the pads, clipped away to deep backward square-leg for couple of runs. Hilfy is still struggling with his line.

Dropped by Paine. Hilfy pushes this well outside off stump, Gambhir reaches out, bat well away from the body, and gets a thick edge. Paine is late to dive to his left and clangs it. It was definitely catchable
run down to third man for a single
length delivery, pushed down the track
slower one, the off cutter, chopped down past point for a single
pushes it well outside off, Gambhir doesn't chase it this time
on the middle stump, from round the stumps, driven to mid-on
on the off stump line, defended to cover
slows up the pace, on the middle and leg, Yuvraj leans forward, tickles it to short backward square-leg  region and they turn back for the second run as well
slightly short in length, Yuvraj goes for the cut but hits it uppishly and just short of the lunging point
Yuvraj goes down town. He skipped down the track and lifted it cleanly over long-off. Interestingly. Ponting had just brought the long-off in for this ball and Yuvraj has taken up the challenge.
goes down on his knee to paddle it away for a single
Done in by the slightly slower one. It was full, it was straight and Yuvraj couldn't keep his drive down. Hilfy swoops to pick up a sharp catch on his follow through. Australia tighten the screws.

Ouch! It crashes against the helmet. Clatter. It was the bouncer, Dhoni just didn't pick it up and just yanked his head away. The ball hit the helmet on the back. He had just turned his face behind and the ball crashed against the bottom of the helmet. Had it gone few inches down, it would have got really nasty. Dhoni smiles after reaching the other end.
leans forward to defend to the off side. There were four fielders outside the circle and hence the no ball call
just outside off stump, guided down to third man
goes back and across to clip it past square-leg
slower one, off cutter, short in length , turned to square-leg for a single
full in length, outside off, Dhoni almost walks into the shot and inside-edges it past the stumps
lunges forward to defend but the ball turns in with bounce to hit the body outside the off stump line. Haurtiz smiles as he likes how much it turned in
leans across, picks the ball from outside off and flicks with the turn to square-leg and rushes across for the first and returns for the second
flighted outside off, almost flicks his off drive, courtesy that bottom-hand, to mid-off

It turned in from outside off, DHoni jabbed it off his gloves behind the wicket. he is not sure where it went and is looking for a run but Paine doesn't pick up the ball cleanly and Dhoni gets back. Had Paine picked it up on the first go, it might have got interesting
stumbles out to drive and is hit on the pads outside off stump
holds his balance so much better this time while coming forward  and drives it forcefully to the cover point boundary
spins down the leg side .. wide
flighted up outside off, Gambhir eases it down to long-off

ooh sharp turn there! And he is not even a regular spinner. It drifted in towards middle and spun sharply. Dhoni gets an outside edge and it flies through vacant slips. Interestingly. Paine was moving towards the leg side; he didn't reckon this bloke could turn it this much!
stretches forward to push it to cover point for a single
comes forward to on drive it to long-on
flighted up, slows up the pace, driven away to long-off
skips down the track and on drives it to long-on for a easy single
flighted full outside off stump, driven down to deep cover
slow through the air, tossed outside off, pushed to extra cover
stretches well across to push it to point for a single
on the off stump line, steered to point for another easy run
flighted around the off stump line, eased down to long-on
on the middle, Gambhir tries to push it to the on side and gets a leading edge
moves down the track and deflects it to midwicket for a single
goes right back to clip it past square-leg and they cross over.
leans forward to defend but pushes outside the line and edges it to his pad. This one went on straight
outside off stump, on a length, Dhoni stretches out well forward to defend
takes a couple of steps down the track and pushes the ball to vacant midwicket. By the the time the man rushes in from the deep, he turns back for the second and makes it just in time
on the leg stump line, Dhoni is wary about getting a leading edge, so waits for the turn before stabbing it down the track
leans forward to work it through covers
spins in from outside off, defended to the off side
flatter, fuller, driven to long-on for yet another run
goes right back to cut it to cover point for a single
leans forward to turn it to close to the on side and by the time Paine rushes after it, they complete the single
on the off stump line, pushed to point fielder
gets well forward to turn it to the on side.
turns in from outside off, from short of length, Gambhir goes back to cut it well to the left of sweeper cover
moves down the track but Vogues shortens the length and Gambhir adjusts to stab it away to the off side
And again. Vogues pushes it shorter and Gambhir manages to push it away past White who dives from his position at short extra cover
moves back to push it towards long-off. . The two are dealing in singles here
slows up the pace, flighted on the off stump line, Gambhir leans forward to work it to long-on
turns in to the middle and leg, nudged past square-leg
comes in with the arm, from round the stumps, on the off stump line, steered to backward point
goes right back to defend a quickish flatter trajectory delivery to the on side
slows up the pace, tosses it up, Dhoni comes down the track but drives it straight back to the bowler
oh neatly done .. it was a flighted delivery on the stumps, Dhoni seemed to merely punch-drive it past the bowler and it kept racing on to the straight boundary.
on the middle and leg, poked around the corner behind square-leg for a single
slightly short in length, cut away to deep point region
moves down the track, takes it on the full and slams it to extra-cover boundary
again skips down the track, the ball is straighter this time and Gambhir pushes it down to long-on
drops it slightly short and Dhoni gets on the back foot to punch it away to long-off
short in length, perhaps expecting Gambhir to step out again but he stays back this time and cuts it away
on the leg and middle, slight turn, nurdled around the corner
on the middle stump line, turns in, worked to short fine-leg region
lands outside off and it keeps a touch low and that throws Gambhir off rhythm and he jabs it out to cover
charges down the track and plays a quality inside-out shot over extra cover. He plays that shot really well. we even saw him take on Muralitharan repeatedly in that fashion.
drags it shorter and its cut past point
worked to right of midwicket, Gambhir wants a single but Dhoni asks him to get back
shout for lbw as Dhoni goes for one of those pokes to the on side but probably struck just outside off stump
angles it across Dhoni, well outside the off stump.
walks right across the stumps, anticipating another one well outside off and shovels it to midwicket
goes for the yorker, ends up as a low dipping full toss on the legs, rolls away to fine-leg. He was out to a similar ball in the first game; the line then was of course on middle
on the middle and leg, turned to backward square-leg for a single
again pushed down the leg side and Paine collects
on the off stump line, guided down to third man and reaches his fifty. The team-mates in the dressing room give him a generous applause
full and around the off stump, steered away behind point for a single
just outside the off stump line, again Dhoni tries to tickle it around the corner, misses and it rolls off the pad to short fine-leg region. He was struck outside the line
leans across to push it to point and Johnson throws wide of Paine! Oh dear.. overthrows.
leans forward to flick it away for a single
slightly short, cut away past point
lovely delivery, it drifted in from round the stumps, landed on a length around off and spun away past the defensive poke
goes right back to work the ball off his pads
full in length, around the off stump line, tapped close on the off side, towards backward point and they scamper across

mini drama short in length around the off stump line, pushed to point and they rush across. Ponting has a shy at the non-striker's end and misses. Dhoni collides with Johnson at the other end and he stumbled into the crease. Had the throw hit the stumps, he would have been run out. Dhoni wasn't pleased with the bowler  but Johnson was was well within his rights to go towards the stumps to try collect the throw. It wasn't done deliberately.
outside off stump, cut down to third man
leans forward to tap it away for another quick single
another tip and run from the Indian duo
outside off stump, full in length, driven to sweeper cover
walks right down the track and placed it deliberately to the left of mid-off.  Neatly done. He just opened the bat-face, found the gap and ran the first run very hard
jumps out and turns the length delivery past square-leg
short in length, just outside off stump, chopped down to third man
on the pads, turned to long leg for a single
just outside off stump, Gambhir dabs it to third man
stretches well forward to drive the full delivery well to the left of mid-off and it races away. He hit it uppishly but found the placement
short in length, on the hips, poor delivery, tucked away to fine-leg boundary.
on the middle and leg , worked to deep square-leg region for couple of runs
fullish, angling away from Gambhir who tries to run it down to third man and is beaten. He is not happy with himself, suggests he should have driven it straight in the V
bouncer around the  leg stump, Gambhir ducks.
short delivery, climbs around the off stump, tapped down to third man
really full delivery, Dhoni doesn't' lean forward and hence, mistimes the drive
outside off stump line, cut away through the off side. 100 of the partnership comes up.
leans forward to tap it towards backward point. There is a direct hit at the non striker's end and it runs away from an extra run
slower, off cutter, allows to come to him before working it down to third man. 200 up now
on the off stump line, pushed to the off side
length delivery around the off stump, pushed through covers
angling away from Gambhir who tries to pick up another run to third man but doesn't get bat on ball
outside off stump and Dhoni carves it really hard but straight to backward point. The pace meant Vogues couldn't stop it cleanly
leans forward to work into gaps on the leg side for yet another single
bangs it in short, doesn't climb all that high and Dhoni pulls it to deep midwicket
again hurls it short and this one climbs higher, around chest-high, Gambhir takes his eyes off the ball as he fends it to the on side
goes for the yorker but drifts outside leg, stabbed past square-leg
bouncer just outside off stump, Dhoni shapes to pull but pulls out from the shot. The umpire has given it a wide. Harsh call.
leans forward to drive it to mid-on
short of a good length delivery outside the off stump, Gambhir stays back and taps it away on the off side and they scamper through for a single. Excellent running between the wickets
fifty! punched off the back-foot to deep cover, gets it wide of the fielder in the deep and they comfortably come back for the second
again driven of the back-foot to deep cover, just a single on this occasion

short of a good length delivery, on the middle and off stump line - Gambhir tries to work it away on the leg side but fails to make contact and the ball rolls away off the pad. Dhoni calls early and once again they scamper through for a well judged single
defended outside the off stump, watchfully played
short of a good length delivery, Dhoni stands tall and punches it away on the off side
from round the stumps, full in length, outside off, sliced away to wide third man
short in length, straightening outside off stump, Dhoni tries to punch it to the off side but edges it to square-leg and they rush back for the second run
leans forward to push it to mid-on
on the middle and leg, edges it to his pad and the ball rolls behind square-leg
swing and a miss. It was a full in length outside off, Dhoni was on the back foot and tried to carve it away hard but no wood on leather

almost caught and bowled and Gambhir is run out! Confusion there! It was the slower one and Dhoni was beaten by it and scooped it just over the leaping Siddle. Gambhir had rushed off ; Hauritz swooped on the ball from mid-off and threw in a direct hit at the non-striker's end to remove Gambhir. Australia continue to impress in the field.
around the off stump, from round the stumps, pushed through cover point for a single
slower in the air, drops it short and Dhoni slashes it to the cover boundary. He waited for the ball to arrive before slapping it really hard.
turns in, shoveled away towards long-on
beaten outside off stump. It was just outside off, turns slightly away, Raina shaped to defend but ...
back of length, Raina goes back to cut it past point for a single
slower, turns in from outside off, cut away to deep point region
length delivery on the off stump line, Dhoni stays back to guide it to point
fuller in length, outside off, Dhoni goes for his slash drive and edges it down to third man
bounces it short but slips it down the leg side. Raina jumped back, trying to turn it to fine-leg but doesn't connect
goes back to steer it to right of backward point where Vogues makes a tumbling stop to prevent the batsmen from taking a single
One slip i place for Raina. It landed on a length, moved in towards middle and leg, Raina tries to work it to the on side and gets a leading edge back down the track
short in length, bouncing in on the off and middle line, defended to cover
full in length, timed sweetly down the track and Siddle lunges to make a half-stop
floated on the off stump line, pushed away towards point for a quick single
on the leg and middle, turned past square-leg for a easy single
turns in from outside off, pushed wide of point
edged but wide of slip. It turned from the middle and off line, from round the stumps, got the edge on the hesitant poke but didn't go to hands
slightly short, cut to point
comes in with the arm, Raina leans forward to block it in front of him
goes on the back foot to work it past square-leg
turns in from outside off, forced away to sweeper cover
stretches forward to tap it to cover for a single
floated well outside off, Raina goes back and across to cut it well to deep backward point
takes a couple of steps down the track, Voges slows up the pace and Raina tickles it around the corner to short fine-leg region
on the middle and leg, wristed to backward square-leg region and retains the strike
lunges forward and across, the ball dips on him and strikes the pad; well outside off stump, though
stays back to pick up a single with a punchy dab towards deep midwicket
nice delivery, on a length outside off, spinning away, Raina thinks about pushing at it before taking his bat away from the line
straighter, on the middle, nurdled to short fine-leg region
fuller, tad quicker, defended on the front foot
floats it well outside off and it goes on straight; Dhoni lunges across, trying to tap it to point for a single but is beaten. Paine quickly whips the bails off but Dhoni was in
wayward delivery down the leg side and Paine does well to make a diving half-stop
from round the stumps to the right-hander, driven towards mid-off for a single
goes right back, jumps to get on top of the bounce and taps it close on the off side and Dhoni calls him over for a quick single
on the middle, worked to midwicket
slower one outside off stump, Dhoni is through with his cut shot early and the ball bounces once before it reaches Paine
fuller, homing in on the off stump, driven to sweeper cover
backs away to the leg side and carves the short delivery over covers to pick up three runs.
clears his front leg and goes for a big slog-swing across the line but doesn't connect well; the ball rolls back to the bowler
short delivery and Raina jumps to defend it down to the off side
short delivery again, Raina tries to slog-pull but can't connect. Another dot ball.
moves outside leg stump and goes for a big drive but mistimes it down to long-on.
short in length, bouncing in towards middle and off, Dhoni can only push it back to the bowler
length delivery outside off, Dhoni goes for his drive and carves it away .. He doesn't quite connect well but finds the gap between extra cover and mid-off and this outfield is really fast
Raina breaks free of the shackles with a swing to square-leg boundary. It drifted towards the pad and Raina swung it away
slower one, on the middle, defended to the on side

clears the front leg and went for the big swing to the on side. He found more elevation than distance. It went really high in the air but no one in wide deep midwicket and it bounces away to the boundary.
moves well outside leg, Mitch tries to follow him with a short-of-length delivery, guided down to third man
from round the stumps now to Dhoni, back of length around off, cut away to backward point
on the middle stump line, squeezed out straight to backward point
the lifting delivery, chest-high, on the middle and leg, fended away towards backward point. Dhoni rushes across for a single and Raina makes it in time with a dive
length delivery this time, tapped towards extra cover for a single

Another one that falls safely. It was the bouncer, Raina had moved outside leg and top-edged his pull but this is a big ground and it falls short of deep square-leg. Siddle thought it would go to hands and is disappointed
mistimes the drive to mid-off for just a single.
moves outside leg stump, Siddle goes for the base of leg stump, Raina crouches to dab it to third man
length delivery on the off stump, Dhoni goes for the swing over mid-on and ends up dragging it to deep square-leg region. Fine tight over from Siddle
Whack. It was a length delivery this time and Raina heaved it to wide long-on region. Hauritz tries valiantly with a dive but can't stop it cleanly and the ball rolled to the ropes
slower one, around off, Raina waits on the front foot, opens the bat-face and steers it to right of backward point

Crashed away. A short delivery from round the stumps and Dhoni plays a crunchy pull shot to wide midwicket boundary. The crowd applaud the boundary and roar as they see the no ball signal and realise its going to be a Free hit next ball .
Violence. That has been killed. It was a short-of-length delivery, a slower one, Dhoni waited for it and flat-batted a thrashing heave to the straight boundary
Dhoni throws the kitchen sink at this one as well. IT was outside off and he carved it high towards the extra-cover boundary. The sweeper cover comes in to kick it away
moves outside leg, Johnson fires in a bouncer on the middle stump line and Raina allows it to go through to the keeper. He then suggests he should have played a upper cut
on the rib cage, Raina swivels to swat it to deep square-leg region. 18 runs in this massive over.
moves again well outside leg, Hilfy follows him and a cramped up Raina pushes it to extra cover
low dipping full toss, Dhoni was walking down the track and almost yorks himself and makes contact with the bottom of the bat; the ball rolls towards long-off
fires in really full, dug out towards Ponting at short extra cover
yorker length, just short of the blockhole may be, on the leg stump line, stabbed away to the on side for a single
That typical bottom-handed twirl from Dhoni is back. He picked the length delivery from the off stump and dispatched it to wide long-on.
leans across, tries to paddle sweep it away but doesn't connect well. He shakes his head in disappointment
really full delivery, punched down to long-on.
100 up and brought up in his inimitable style. The crowd go mad. That bottom-hand powered strike again. It was full around the off stump and he carves it over long-off.
Oh boy another big hit. Dhoni went for the sliced drive this time and it went high in the air and just managed to clear long-off. The delirious crowd go berserk. The noise is deafening.
short in length, cut away hard and the point  fielder takes some pace off the ball
yorker length outside off, Dhoni reaches out to slice it to right of point where Voges makes another tumbling stop
almost yorker length on the middle and off, dug out to cover point
Bosh.  Full pitched delivery around off stump and Raina carves it high over the bowler and it races away
Crash bang wallop. Raina cleared the front foot and swung the full toss over wide midwicket boundary. The camera pans to a grim Ponting who chews his gum as he stares ahead at nothing in particular
oh excellent placement .. he moved outside leg and square drove it superbly to deep backward point

Even better. Fifty up in no time. It was the bouncing short-of-length delivery on the middle and off, Raina arched back, opened the bat-face ala Ranatunga and late cut it through the vacant slip region
low full toss, mistimes the drive to long-off
length delivery and Dhoni wants to heave it over long-on but goes really hard into the shot and ends up dragging it off the inner half of the bat to deep midwicket
short in length, on the off stump, punched away to deep cover
yorker length, dipping in front of the lunging Raina who jabs it to the on side for a single
That could have taken out Watto. It was a low full toss - the disease is back - and Dhoni thrashes it past the startled bowler who manages to get away from the line of fire
full delivery, edges the big drive towards midwicket for a run
low dipping full toss, swung away wide of deep midwicket for couple of runs
goes for the yorker again, dips in front of Raina who reaches out, tries to take it on the full and makes contact with the bottom of that bat; the ball rolls away to long-off
moves outside leg, Siddle follows him with a full toss,  Raina, who is cramped for room, shovels it  away towards long-off
fullish, on the leg stump line, Dhoni ensures that the front foot doesn't come in the way and flicks it to deep square-leg boundary. That bottom-hand working overtime.
fine yorker on the base of middle stump, dug out back to the bowler and Ponting applauds the effort
another fine full delivery, jabbed away to the on side
moves outside leg, Siddle fires it really full outside off, Dhoni reaches out to jam it past backward point
Fab shot. He moved outside leg, waited for the full ball, crouched to flick it to deep backward square-leg boundary. He expected the full delivery and was ready
from round the stumps but slips in a wide delivery outside off stump. Raina walks across to punch Dhoni's gloves

dropped by Ponting Dhoni went for the big bottom-hand powered lofted drive but sliced it away really high in the air. Ponting back-pedaled from cover but didn't judge it well and the ball dipped behind him
outside off stump, Raina runs it down to third man.

Dhoni falls after a superbly paced knock. It was a full delivery on the off stump line, he tried to whip it across the line but edged it to right of Paine who takes a tumbling catch. Dhoni gets a standing ovation from the crowd. He started off ,dealing in singles, before he turned violent in the end
fullish, outside off, Harbhajan slices it to right of wide third man for a single

Another sharp catch from Paine. Raina edged the intended lofted hit to long-on and the ball appeared to be flying over Paine who leaped to bring it back to earth. What a gem of a cameo from Raina, though. Bosh. Biff. Wham bham stuff from him.

PK is run out full in length around the off stump line, turned to thrid man. PK came back for the second run ... Again Paine does a fine job to collect the slightly wide throw and flick it away to the stumps to run out Praveen Kumar

inn2.comm: full delivery, bit of movement, on the middle, defended back down the track
again moving in to the middle, deflected to midwicket
swings away from the off stump, Watson tries to slash it away but doesn't connect
full in length, on the middle and leg, Watson holds his balance to glance it away to the fine-leg boundary. The fielder was very square and he couldn't come across in time
length delivery, moving away from the middle stump line, squeezed out to left of backward point
length delivery on the off and middle line, Watson stays back to defend to the off side
short in length around the off stump line, defended to the off side
full and swinging in, trying for the lbw but drifts to middle and leg, flicked away hard but straight to Gambhir at square-leg
another one swinging in, Watson has had problems with those deliveries in the past, but manages to stab this one to short fine-leg region
back of length, on the middle, pushed towards Ishant at mid-on for a quick single
fires in the bouncer on the off stump line, gets into the position to pull before withdrawing from the shot.
full in length, on the middle and off line, defended back to the bowler
back of length, lands on middle and curves away, Watson wants to punch it to the off side but edges it to the on side
this one swings in and strikes the pad but it was going down leg side. Shout for lbw but umpire Shavir Tarapore has a easy decision to make
And this one curves away - he is mixing up things here, and  is beaten on the attempted slash
leans forward to push it to covers for a single
width on offer outside off and Watson, with his weight on the back foot, carves it past diving Jadeja at backward point.
length delivery on the middle, pushed back to Nehra who lunges to his right to stop
back of length, on the off stump line, tries to run it down to third man but can't find the placement properly
on a length around the off stump, mistimes the punchy stroke towards Yuvraj at mid-off
slants this one across Watson who tries to cut it but can't connect
tries to swing it back into the right-hand batsman but slips down the leg side
stays back to work this one Sehwag at short midwicket. Sehwag threatens to have a shy at the non-striker's end and has a laugh about it with Paine
again deflected to Sehwag who has a shy at the stumps this time and Yuvraj backs up at mid-off
shuffles across the stumps and flicks the ball from the middle to right of Nehra at deep backward square-leg
full in length, on the middle, pushed towards mid-on for a single
lands on a length around off stump, moves away, pushed out to cover. Slip and leg gully in place
slightly slower one around the off and middle, jabbed out to cover
short in length, around the off stump, Paine stays back to pull it high over midwicket.
The leg stump goes for a walk and PK is thrilled. It was fuller this time and the ball cut back in from outside off. Paine went for the big swing over mid-on and edged it to his leg stump. 20 for 1.
leans forward to drive to mid-on where Ishant has a shy at the non-striker's end but misses
angling away from Ponting who shoulders arms
on the pads, clipped to Praveen at deep backward square-leg
straightening on the middle stump line, Watson leans forward, gets the bat in front of the pad to defend.
on the middle and leg line, back of length, Watson whips it past Gambhir at square-leg and the outfield is too quick
slightly short in length, skids on towards off stump, Watson goes for the pull but mistimes it completely and the ball rolls to Sehwag at short midwicket
leans forward to work it away past square-leg
outside off stump, shapes away, timed sweetly but can;t quite pierce off-side field
not all that far from the off stump but Watson chops it away for a single
lovely delivery, lands on a length on the middle and curves to middle and off, Ponting stretches forward to defend
curves away from the off stump line, Ponting gets forward to push it to mid-off
on the off stump line, from back of length, Ponting goes back to punch it to cover point
bangs it in short and slants it away across Watson who lets it go through to the keeper. Both batsmen get together for a chat
fuller in length, straightening on the middle stump, aiming for that lbw, but Watson gets the bat in front of the bat and deflects the ball to Sehwag at short midwicket
length delivery, pushed to left of Sehwag and to right of mid-on for a single
Lovely off drive. So easy on the eye. He leaned into the shot and caressed it past the non-striker
slightly short in length and moving away from Ponting who goes for the pull but doesn't connect
short in length, on the middle stump line, Ponting goes right back and wrists it between short midwicket and square-leg. And he has timed that one really well.
run out missed. It was pushed towards midwicket and they rushed across. Gambhir with the throw but misses the sticks at the non-striker's end.
around the off stump line, steered to Jadeja at backward point
on the middle stump line, full in length, Ponting gets forward, gets his bat around the pad and flicks it uppishly towards midwicket
full and outside off, Ponting is beaten on the drive. Perhaps, he went too hard into the shot and the bat came down in an awkward angle
goes for the slower one but slips down the leg side
full in length, around the off stump line, coming in a bit, Ponting shapes to punch it on the up towards cover but edges it to mid-on
straightens on the middle stump line, pushed out to mid-on

Ishant strikes first ball. It kicked up high from short of length, Watson was pressing forward before he tried go back and dab it to third man. However, he was done in by the extra bounce. At the last minute, he tried to adjust by taking out the bottom hand off the handle but only succeeded in guiding the ball straight and low to Tendulkar at first slip
short of length delivery outside off and left alone
short in length and outside off stump and White lashes out at the width, forcing it through cover point
short in length and outside off stump, left alone
length delivery rushing through the off-stump channel, Dhoni collects
full in length, on the middle, turned down to mid-on

trapped right in front. PK has taken out the big wicket of the Australian captain and the crowd roar their approval. It was a length delivery that cut in from just outside off. Ponting was on the front foot, looking to drive on the up but is beaten by the inward movement. He was struck in line on the off and middle line and he has to go. PK ran straight to Ishant to celebrate, followed by wildly happy Raina and the other team-mates
full in length, moving away from Hussey who shoulders arms
lands in on a length around off and shapes it away, left alone
superb delivery, luring Hussey forward before leaving him very late past the outside edge
And again. PK in middle of a fine spell here. It lands full in length on the off stump line and curves away, Hussey is beaten as he tries to push forward to defend
gets this one to straighten on the middle and Hussey watchfully plays it down to the off-side of the pitch.
full in length, lands outside off and rushes on to Dhoni
And again. White covers his off stump and allows the length delivery to pass through to the keeper
just outside off stump, goes through straight, White lets it pass him
really full, on the middle, gunning for that lbw, White is ready, makes sure that front foot isn't pressed across and pushes the ball down to mid-on
back of length, outside off stump, punched away to backward point

good probing delivery, cutting in from around the off stump line, White lunged forward, took the bottom-hand off the handle and stabbed the ball off the inner edge to right of square-leg where a tumbling save is made by Tendulkar
lands full in length, on the middle and off, shapes away slight, leans forward to defend
from slightly wide of the crease, length delivery that moves away late, squeezed out to backward point
full in length, some width outside off and driven down to deep cover
pushes it across Hussey who cuts it down to Gambhir at deep cover
short in length, around the off stump, moving away, punched down to mid-off
slightly slower one, full and drifting in towards middle and leg, White chips it in the air but well clear of mid-on and it runs away to the boundary
full delivery, around off stump line, driven to left of short cover where Raina makes a half-stop
length delivery straightening on the off stump line, good bounce there, dabbed down to third man
good ball, length delivery skidding on straight to the middle, Hussey stays back to push it away to the on side
back of length, bounces towards the off and middle line, defended to the off side
just outside off stump, Hussey opens the bat-face and runs it down to third man
full in length and in that corridor, left alone
overpitched outside off stump and Hussey crashes it through the off-side field.
on a length, turns away from Hussey who goes right back to cut it past point. It landed just outside off and spun away further
Three in a row. Husseeeyyyyyyyy. It was short in length, quicker, flatter and Hussey unfurls a fine crunchy cut shot
even more quicker, but slips down the leg side
skids on quickly just outside off, dabbed away ..
slower, on the middle and leg, defended to midwicket
on the middle, straightens, defended on the front foot
back of length delivery but some width on offer and White crashes it on the up and gets it past to left of diving Nehra at mid-off
length delivery on the off stump line and moves away lightly, left alone
full in length, on the middle and off stump line, White leans forward to push it back to the bowler
banged in short, on the middle, a surprised Cameron White jumps to fend it away to backward point
length delivery outside off stump, punched on the up to deep cover
sharp well-directed bouncer, on the middle stump line, Hussey is late on the pull and it flies of the top-edge high over Dhoni
on the middle stump line, turned past square-leg
lands it short in length, cut away to covers where there is  fumble by Raina ..
full, turns in, worked to the on side
turns in a bit more than White anticipated; he was looking to cut but jabs it away in the end
picks it from the off stump and sweeps it to Nehra at deep backward square-leg
full in length, driven down to long-off
full in length, around the off stump, steered to backward point
back of length, just outside off stump, cut down to third man
full in length, shapes away, squeezed to left of backward point to Jadeja
pushes it across Hussey who mistimes the cut to Raina at cover
back of length, on the off and middle line, Hussey presses back, taps the ball close on the off side and off he goes for the single
length delivery on the middle stump line, defended to the on side
lands slightly short in length, cut away to sweeper cover
comes down the track, Harbhajan shortens the length, squeezed out to backward square-leg
on the off stump line, skids on from short of length, cut down to sweeper cover
flighted outside off stump, full in length, White doesn't quite lean forward, just pushes his bat away from the body and edges it down the track
tries to come down the track but has to adjust to the shortening of the length and jabs it away
eased down to long-on for a single
short in length but skids on towards middle, White crouches quickly to keep it out
slower, fuller outside off, pushed out to point
on the leg stump line, slower through the air, Hussey is through with the flick a touch early and is struck on the pad
quicker, arm ball, skidding on to the off, defended to the on side
moves down the track but can't reach the pitch of the ball and turns it to midwicket
on the middle, moving on straight, pushed back to the bowler
slightly short in length, just outside off, cut away to deep cover
skips down the track but is beaten in flight and by the shortening of the length and he adjusts to stab it to midwicket
stays at his crease and defends the off break back down the track
fetches it from the off stump and sweeps it down to Nehra at deep backward square-leg
moves right back to dab it behind square-leg for a single

White has been repeatedly trying to get down the track but has been unable to reach the pitch of the ball. And he has adjusted by jabbing it away,. But this time, he tries to go through with the shot and only succeeds in lobbing a dolly to Raina at straight ish midwicket.
around the off stump line, pushed wide of Sehwag at cover for a single
lands on a length around off stump and turns away, steered wide of first slip
fuller, just outside off, steered very fine through vacant slip region
on the middle and leg, turned past square-leg
on the leg and middle line, turns to get a leading edge to cover
slower through the air, really full in length, pushed out to Raina at midwicket
full in length, eased down to long-off
on the off stump line, defended to the on side
slower, turns in, deflected wide of midwicket
on the leg stump line, goes for the sweep but  misses
just outside off, skids on, Hussey gets a bottom edge on the cut and it bounces behind the wicket
short in length, quicker, cut away to sweeper cover
floated full outside off stump, steered through backward point for couple of runs
goes for the reverse sweep, sends it straight to short third man where PK makes a mess of it ...
goes for another reverse sweep but Yuvraj slows up the pace further and the ball rolls away to midwicket
outside off stump, cut to backward point region for a single
leans forward to push it to cover point
on the middle and off, punched away to long-off
on the off stump line, Voges pings long-off
stays back to punch it to the on side and Harbhajan makes a diving stop
turns in, worked to midwicket
turns in slowly, wristed to backward square-leg and they rush back for the second run
low dipping full toss, jammed away to cover
lands on a length on the middle, turns down leg for a wide
turns in from outside off, hits the pad outside the line of off stump
slows up the pace, on the middle, flicked to right of midwicket where Raina makes a diving stop
floated outside off, driven to Sehwag at cover
quicker, on the leg stump line, turned to midwicket
slower, turns in to the middle stump, pushed away to Sehwag
on the leg stump line, pushed to left of  Raina at midwicket for a quick single
on the off stump line, driven past the diving Raina to long-off
quicker one, shorter in length, skids on, mistimes the pull straight to Raina at short midwicket
turns in slowly to the off and middle line, clipped to Gambhir at deep midwicket
stays back to punch it to cover
this one curves back in with the arm, Hussey is late in picking it but manages to squeeze it out to square-leg
slower through the air, flighted outside off, defended on the front foot
spins in from outside off, defended to the off side
flighted on the middle stump line, flicked to right of Gambhir, running in from deep midwicket
on the middle stump line, goes on with the arm, punched back to Yuvraj
slows up the pace, again goes on with the arm, Hussey is beaten, playing for the non-existent turn
quicker, on the off stump line, cut away to cover
on the middle stump line, dragged down to Gambhir at deep midwicket
slip in place for Voges who drives this full delivery to long-off
on the middle and leg, turned towards Gambhir at deep midwicket for couple of runs
leans forward to defend to the off side
leans forward to drive it past the bowler
on the off stump line, cut away to sweeper cover
turns in to the middle and leg, worked past square-leg
just outside off stump, Hussey cuts it past diving Yuvraj at point and no one in the deep to cover up... a boundary after a long time
big swing and a miss. It was flighted outside off, Hussey went for the big slog sweep and missed
just outside off, slightly short in length, cut to right of Gambhir at sweeper cover
goes for the reverse sweep and connects well this time. He hit that short-of-length delivery to deep backward point boundary. 50 up for Hussey. 26th ODI fifty
goes for another reverse sweep but top edges it short of PK at short third man
quicker one on the pads, swatted down to PK at fine leg
goes right back to defend to the off side
flighted on the middle and leg, flicked away for a single
floated full in length, pushed out to midwicket
turns in to Hussey who deflects it to midwicket

He took out Ponting with a good delivery in the last game; takes out Hussey with a lovely one tonight. It landed on a length outside off and turned in sharply. Hussey chose to go back instead of coming forward and was surprised by the amount of turn. It went right through the bat and pad gap to disturb the furniture.
turns in to the middle, worked to square-leg
leans forward to on drive the full delivery to long-on
quickish, on the off stump line, defended to cover
tossed up slowly, driven through the on side for a single
on the middle, coming in with the arm, whipped towards deep midwicket
slows up the pace, flighted outside off, defended to point
floated on the off and middle, driven down to long-on
on the middle and off line, guided to backward point
flighted ever so slowly outside off, driven to cover where Raina fumbles to give away runs
outside off stump, skids on straight, cut away to deep backward point region
the arm-ball, Voges is on the back foot and pushes it to the on side
slower, fuller, on the off stump, edges the drive to the on side
quicker, flatter, on the leg and middle, deflected wide of midwicket
threatens to come out but changes mind and just stabs it to the on side
leans well forward to drive a flighted delivery to long-off
fuller, quicker, turned to midwicket
on the middle and leg, flicked to right of square-leg where Jadeja makes a diving stop
fetches it from well outside off and paddles it away
on the middle and leg, turned to Raina at midwicket
on the off stump line this time, eased to long-off

loud shout for lbw but turned down. It turned in from the off stump line, goes past the attempted pull and hits the pad high ...It hit him on the off stump line and hawk eye suggests it wuold have hit the middle ...
slightly short in length, outside off, cut down to the off side
leans forward to chip the flighted delivery uppishly to cover and Raina has a shyt at the non-striker's end ad misses. had he hit, the batsman would have been run out
PK makes a mess at long-on It was lofted straight to PK who took the catch and stepped back and threads on the boundary ropes. He took it inside and couldn't avoid stepping back
drops it short and Vogues backs away to the leg side and cuts it really hard to the point boundary
flighted from round the stumps, driven to cover
from round the stumps, the batsman moves well outside the leg stump and cuts but cant' pierce the off-side field
on the pads, tries to sweep and collects a leg bye
goes back to punch it to long-on
turned to short fine-leg region
spins in from outside , placed wide of cover for a single
goes for the big sweep but misses it completely; the ball lands outside off and turns away
again goes for the sweep but hits it straight to deep midwicket
steps out and lofts it well to the right of long-on where PK tries to push it back to the stumps but pushes it beyond the ropes
He charges out again but this time, Jadeja gets the ball to go straight with the arm, outside off stump, past the big swing, and Marsh is stranded down the track
full outside off stump, edges the drive to the on side
on the middle and leg, turned to midwicket
down the leg side and Sahiba extends his arms
moves outside leg, Harbhajan slows up the pace, and Johnson waits and waits before forcing it through extra cover
fuller, on the off stump line, squeezed to right of backward point. Confusion between the two batsmen but Johnson is sent back in time
moves outside leg, and mistimes the cut to Yuvraj at cover
has had enough of trying to get it through the off side field and lifts this superbly over long-on..  big hit
slogs and gets away with a miscue, the ball flies up in the air and lands between midwicket and mid-on safely
good ball, flatter this time, pushes Johnson back and he works the ball to midwicket
bowled! Voges gets across too far, exposing the stumps, and tries to sweep from outside off stump but the ball clips his front pad and glove and rolls onto the sticks
slower now, tossed up outside off and he pushes it to cover
flat on off stump and swept between square leg and midwicket
change of pace, full on the stumps, pushed to mid-on for a quick run
tossed up on the stumps, turns in, he plays and misses
tossed up and driven back to the bowler
flatter ball and he punches it back off the back foot
too fine and he works it to square leg
too short and Johnson hits it off the back foot past cover
short and down the pads so Hauritz clips it away for a single
takes couple of steps down the track and drives to long-off
moves outside leg and pulls the ball straight past the non-striker and long-off is wide and can't cut it off
on the middle and leg, turned to Yuvraj at short fine-leg
comes down the track, Jadeja shortens the length and its defended back down the pitch
charges down the track and crashes the flighted delivery over the bowler's head and to the straight boundary
moves outside leg, Nehra follows him with a very full delivery, driven down to long-on
banged in short, upper cut towards third man and Harbhajan rushes in to take the catch but it drops short of him and bounces past his lunge
bouncer on the middle stump line, ducked under
punches this length delivery to mid-off
swing and a miss. He moved outside leg, had a big swing towards long-on. bat meets air and the ball bounces over middle stump
yorker length around the off and middle, edged to the pad
again, moves outside leg stump, has a big slog but doesn't connect. The ball flies past the leg stump
length delivery on the off stump line, punched to mid-off
moves outside leg, mistimes the drive to right of Tendulkar at mid-off
short in length, on the middle and leg, jabbed to the on side. Ishant rushes after it and flicks from very close to the stumps but misses! The batsman, though, was in by then
backs away to push it to deep cover
fires across a bouncer, pulled down to Jadeja at fine-leg region
slower one just outside off stump, steered down to third man
ouch. The short delivery and Hauritz tries to duck but it doesn't climb all that much and whooshes past the face ..
moves outside leg and drives to long-off
Clatter. The off stump has been uprooted. Johnson has a slog across the line, misses, and hears the death rattle.
Slip in place now. full in length on the middle, worked wide of midwicket.
moves outside leg, goes for a pull but the ball flashes past his blade
again, moves outside leg but this time goes down ground and heaves the length delivery to wide long-on boundary
fullish, moves past the poke and strikes the pad, missing leg stump, though
full in length, drags it to midwicket
bouncer on the middle, not quite in position but manages to swat it away over square-leg
fired in short again, outside off, Siddle tries to upper cut it but edges it to Dhoni. Nine down now.
fuller delivery, turned past square-leg
slips in a slower one, through the shot early but manages to chip it high over mid-off .. Tendulkar rushes back but couldn't' quite reach it
full delivery outside off, driven past the bowler and Jadeja cleans up from long-off
banged in short and heaved away to the midwicket boundary ..
another short delivery, another pull  but this time PK moves quickly to his right and makes a fine tumbling stop
moves outside leg, slips in a slower one outside off and Dhoni collects
really full delivery on the middle, driven down to long-on
really full delivery, short of the blockhole, pushed out to cover
short in length, bunted out to mid-off
full delivery on the off, driven to mid-off
played to Praveen kumar at deep cover and PK fires in a wild throw way above Dhoni's head .. extra runs
moves down the leg side, brushes the thigh pad and Dhoni makes a fine diving take
banged in short and well outside off, cut and a miss ..
length delivery on the middle and off, pushed out to short extra cover
full in length, on the middle, pushed out to long-off
slower one on the middle, dragged down to midwicket
bangs it in short and Hilfy smashes it to wide long-on boundary
fuller, lofted to wide long-on region for couple of runs
slips in a slower one, mistimes the drive back to PK who fumbles ...
short in length, pushed out to extra cover
on the middle stump line, defended back to the bowler

Hilfenhaus is run out. He went down the track and dragged it to midwicket and set off for a single. He is sent back but too late. Yuvraj flicks it to Dhoni who breaks the stumps. India win by 99 runs and the series stands 1-1.
